divs: Sighting DetailsAbout 4 a.m. looking toward Orion (southeast) observed object translucent orangish, in the shape of half a butterfly moving rapidly in arc and then disappeared.
Summary: reporting on behalf of my sister who does not have computer, it is ok to contact her. saw a translucent object orangish in color shaped like half butterfly as she was looking southeast toward Orion, it made an arc around her and then disappeared.
